  "body": "<p>Hello again! This is Violeta Scrap, and today I want to show you a Layout that I have created with some of my holiday pictures.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595290271374-MON7FOEKFCTUG3JTFRB0/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>As base for the Layout I have used a paper of different stripes of colors from the “Hustle &amp; Heart” collection where I have put a white basic cardstock of 11,5”x11,5”.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595290291516-AU0ATALLKCIC8NUYVQTE/06b-HEY%2BHEY%2BSWEET%2BLAYOUT%2B2.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>In this Layout I have used eight photographs of different sizes. Some of the photographs are displayed under the another. To create this, I have used some patterned papers from the “Hustle &amp; Heart” collection. With the papers I have created a flap so I can glue a photograph inside and another one outside.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595290312574-J306TSDPS1Y1ZF1T3XIB/06c-HEY%2BHEY%2BSWEET%2BLAYOUT%2B3.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For the title of the Project I have combined a chipboard from the “On a Whim” collection with a foam word from the Thickers of the “Hustle &amp; Heart” collection. In addition, I have included some die cuts from the collection “On a Whim” as decorative elements in different areas of the project and some chipboard elements, also from the “On a Whim” collection.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595290330427-IWGZYRWPE2AJUUAJA55V/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>As a decorative element, I have also used some transparent stickers that I have placed on one of the photographs, and I have added some pink-shaped glossy puffy stickers too, which combines very well with the colors of the project.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595290348413-7MMKXXCDKLB585QSFM3L/06e-HEY%2BHEY%2BSWEET%2BLAYOUT%2B5.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Lastly, I have added some drops of blue paint, that I have made with some of my spray paints and I have splattered in a couple of areas of the project, as a decorative touch.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595290377678-SQCE52A0NHSGB4OGRCXI/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This Project can be useful for you to get ideas for those layouts that you want to create using several pictures in an easy way, even if the pictures are from your holidays or from a special occasion.</p><p>Violeta Scrap</p><p><a href=\"http://violetascrap.com/\">Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/violeta_scrap/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/violeta_scrap\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VioletaScrap/\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/VioletaScrap\">YouTube</a></p><p>Supplies: Hustle &amp; Heart- 12x12 Double Sided Paper – The bright side (341874), Hustle &amp; Heart- 12x12 Double Sided Paper – Floral sensation (341871), Hustle &amp; Heart - Thickers – The Lucky Ones (341887), On a whim - Thickers - LOL (378746), On a whim Collection - Clear Stickers, On a whim Collection - Sticker Book (378748), On a whim Collection - Die-cut shapes (378750), Hustle &amp; Heart – Glossy Puffy Stickers (341889)</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing, Violeta! Other Design Team member posts can be found </em><a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/?category=amy+tangerine+design+team\"><em>here</em></a><em>. Shop HUSTLE &amp; HEART now! Check your local retailer and online at </em><a href=\"https://shop.amytangerine.com/shop/hustle-heart-collection\"><em>our shop</em></a><em>, </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/AThustleandheart\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vJOlKd\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p><p><em>Disclosure: Some of the links above are affiliate links. I receive a small percentage of sales at no cost to you. My creative partners and I really appreciate your continued support and every little bit helps me to bring you consistent content!</em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
